# openai-simple

A simple way to communicate with GPT 3.



## Installation

Install with pip.

```bash
pip install openai-simple  
```
    






## Usage/Examples

```javascript
import openai_simple

openai_simple.get_answer("Who is Bill Clinton?", 100, API_KEY)
```
(100 is max tokens in the response.)


